videos.description: Seventh Woods gets around a screen and lobs an alley-oop to Sterling Manley, who throws it down in the 1st half vs. Elon.
videos.headline: Manley puts in dunk off alley-oop pass

videos.description: UNC's Luke Maye jab steps and hits a step-back jumper over an Elon defender in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Maye knocks down step-back jumper

videos.description: UNC's Seventh Woods misses, but freshman Nassir Little throws down a putback dunk before the 1st-half buzzer.
videos.headline: Little rises up for powerful dunk to end 1st half
